headline: Pediatrix Medical's Q2 Earnings Beat on Strong Patient Volumes
summary: MD's Q2 earnings benefit from higher patient volumes and a declining expense level. It now projects 2025 adjusted EBITDA within $245-$255 million, up from the prior view of $220-$240 million.
